    • Method Detail

      • readFromFile

        public void readFromFile(java.lang.String filePath)
                  throws java.lang.Exception
        This method read data from file placed into resources folder and transform it to Visitor object. Then transformed objects are saving to VisitorRepository object. Blank lines are skipped. File format is very important. Make sure, that file content looks like this: 
             
      ...
      10:00,13:00
      14:00,15:00
      11:00,14:00
      ...
        Parameters:
        filePath - path to file with data
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
